        "Alya a veces me susurra en ruso",
        "가끔씩 툭하고 러시아어로 부끄러워하는 옆자리의 아랴 양"
      ],
      "description": "Masachika Kuse sits next to Alya, a girl of Russian and Japanese descent. She's beautiful, haughty, and an exceptional student, while Masachika is nerdy and known for being a slacker. He's an easy target for her comments in Russian, which she's all too happy to translate—except he can understand what she's really saying!\n<br><br>\n(Source: K Manga)",
