    "Eleceed": {
      "id": 106929,
      "title": {
        "english": "Eleceed",
        "romaji": "Eleceed",
        "native": "일렉시드"
      },
      "synonyms": [
        "Eleceed: Velocidad eléctrica",
        "觉醒吧，铲屎官！",
        "覺醒吧！貓奴"
      ],
      "description": "Jiwoo is a kind-hearted young man who harnesses the lightning quick reflexes of a cat to secretly make the world a better place – one saved little child or foster pet at a time. Kayden is a secret agent on the run, who finds himself stuck in the body of a…um…decidedly fat old fluffy cat. Together, armed with Jiwoo’s super powers and Kayden’s uber-smarts, they’re out to fight those forces who would let evil rule this world. That is, if they can stand each other long enough to get the job done.\n<br><br>(Source: WEBTOONS)",
