    "Solo Leveling": {
      "id": 105398,
      "title": {
        "english": "Solo Leveling",
        "romaji": "Na Honjaman Level Up",
        "native": "나 혼자만 레벨업"
      },
      "synonyms": [
        "I Level Up Alone",
        "Only I Level Up",
        "俺だけレベルアップな件",
        "我獨自升級",
        "Ore dake Level Up na Ken",
        "Поднятие уровня в одиночку",
        "Тільки я візьму новий рівень"
      ],
      "description": "In a world where awakened beings called “Hunters” must battle deadly monsters to protect humanity, Seong Jin-U, nicknamed “the weakest hunter of all mankind,” finds himself in a constant struggle for survival. One day, after a brutal encounter in an overpowered dungeon wipes out his party and threatens to end his life, a mysterious System chooses him as its sole player: Jin-U has been granted the rare opportunity to level up his abilities, possibly beyond any known limits. Follow Jin-U’s journey as he takes on ever-stronger enemies, both human and monster, to discover the secrets deep within the dungeons and the ultimate extent of his powers.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Tappytoon)\n<br><br>\n<i>Note: Includes 22 extra chapters.</i>",
      "status": "FINISHED",
