        "전생했더니 슬라임이었던 건에 대하여"
      ],
      "description": "As players of Monster Hunter and Dungeons & Dragons know, the slime is not exactly the king of the fantasy monsters. So when a 37-year-old Tokyo salaryman dies and wakes up in a world of dragons and magic, he's a little disappointed to find he's become a blind, boneless slime monster.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Kodansha USA)",
