    "101517": {
      "id": 101517,
      "title": {
        "english": "Jujutsu Kaisen",
        "romaji": "Jujutsu Kaisen",
        "native": "呪術廻戦"
      },
      "synonyms": [
        "Sorcery Fight",
        "주술회전",
        "咒术回战",
        "Guerra de Hechiceros",
        "Batalha de Feiticeiros",
        "JJK",
        "มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร",
        "Chú thuật hồi chiến",
        "Магическая битва",
        "La guerra màgica",
        "Prokleté války",
        "咒術迴戰",
        "Contiendas de Brujería",
        "Lanet Savaşları"
      ],
      "description": "Although Yuji Itadori looks like your average teenager, his immense physical strength is something to behold! Every sports club wants him to join, but Itadori would rather hang out with the school outcasts in the Occult Research Club. One day, the club manages to get their hands on a sealed cursed object. Little do they know the terror they’ll unleash when they break the seal…\n<br><br>\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n<br><br>\n<i>Notes:<br>\n- Ranked 1st in Japan's Bookstore Employees Top Manga of 2018.<br>\n- Nominated for the 25th Annual Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize in 2021.<br>\n- Nominated for the 65th Shogakukan Manga Award in the Shounen Category in 2019.<br>\n- Includes one extra chapter.</i>",
