        "romaji": "Chainsaw Man: Buddy Stories",
        "native": "チェンソーマン バディ・ストーリーズ"
      },
      "synonyms": [],
      "description": "Power lives out her favorite anime by becoming a genius detective—or so she wants her “audience” to believe! Denji is along for the ride as her assistant for an investigation into disappearances at a mountain hotel. Other stories center on Quanxi and Kishibe’s relationship nine years after they met, Himeno and Aki’s first assignment together, and Denji, Power, and Aki’s dream trip to Enoshima.\n<br><br>\n(Source: VIZ Media)",
